BFN 

  [Text] Brother Staff Brigadier General Haytham Qasim 
Tahir, the defense minister, carried out an inspection tour this 
afternoon at the Ba Suhayb Military Hospital, during which he 
visited a number of those wounded during the war imposed by 'Ali 
Abdallah Salih on our people and homeland. During his visit to 
the wounded, and his inspection of the hospital, the brother 
defense minister gave instructions on the care to be extended to 
the wounded. He gave instructions that the hospital be supplied 
with everything it required to enable it to provide the sick and 
wounded with optimal services. 
  Following his visit to the Ba Suhayb Military Hospital, 
Staff 
Brigadier General Haytham Qasim Tahir replied to questions posed 
to him by a number of correspondents. He told them that the 
Armed Forces of the Democratic Republic of Yemen had won a 
number of victories on all battlefronts, and that all the 
fighters enjoyed high morale in repulsing the aggressive forces 
of the bloody al-Ahmar clan. 

